    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 1,
      "text": "What is the Cerberus"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 2,
      "text": "Cerberus is a global platform that consists of several repos. These repos are currently being utilized in our TC3XX IDC project."
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 1,
      "text": "How to check if you have Cerberus permissions"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 2,
      "text": "1.Open IDM System to check the Access rights https://rb-im.bosch.com/BOAWeb/welcome"
    },
    {
      "type": "image",
      "src": "https://inside-docupedia.bosch.com/confluence/download/attachments/embedded-page/CARSFW/Cerberus%20Access%20Rights%20Check%20Guideline/image-2023-11-27_9-44-24.png?api=v2",
      "alt": "",
      "local_path": "_images/Cerberus Access Rights Check Guideline/image-2023-11-27_9-44-24.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 2,
      "text": "2.Open XC_Gerrit Item to check if have the Cerberus Access rights (KEY WORD :CERBERUS)"
    },
    {
